  message: <<EOM
Now that GEF CHERI plugins is installed it can be used with gdb(1).

Run the following command in the gef-enabled gdb prompt to load the plugin:

```
gef config gef.extra_plugins_dir %%DATADIR%%
```

In order to load GEF CHERI plugins automatically on gdb(1) launch add the line mentioned
above to ~/.gdbinit:

```
echo "gef config gef.extra_plugins_dir %%DATADIR%%" >> ~/.gdbinit
```
EOM
}
